data.name: label1.Text
data.value: When linked, the current account status can be displayed in real time. Examples of available information : Real-time note, Traveler's Dirty etc...

data.name: IsCountBackground.Text
data.value: Count play time even in the background

data.name: label8.Text
data.value: Format specifications: Can be also specify a folder by using "/" in the destination format. Example: "<UID>/<DATE>-<TIME>" -> Screenshot generated under UID folder The available commands are: <UID> Game account UID (will not change until you restart the game) <DATE> Date in "20XX-XX-XX" display method <TIME> Time in "XX-XX-XX" display method <YEAR> <MONTH> <DAY> : Year, month, day <APM> AM/PM <12H> <24H> 12/24 hours <MIN> <SEC> Minutes and seconds <UNIX> UNIX time <FF> <FFF> <FFFF>... Number of seconds after the decimal point from 2 to 7 digits
